## Proposed Changes

### [MODIFY] `WifiDirectManager.kt`

#### 1. `updateDeviceName()` — tambah prefix `CRK:`
```kotlin
// Line 341 — ubah:
method.invoke(manager, channel, name, ...)
// menjadi:
val carakaName = if (name.startsWith("CRK:")) name else "CRK:$name"
method.invoke(manager, channel, carakaName, ...)
```

#### 2. Tambah `carakaLanPeerMacs: MutableSet<String>` field
Track MAC address device yang sudah terverifikasi via LAN HANDSHAKE.

#### 3. `saveLanPeer()` — simpan MAC ke set
```kotlin
carakaLanPeerMacs.add(hostAddress)  // atau MAC jika bisa
```

#### 4. `onPeersAvailable()` — rewrite auto-connect dengan 3-tier filter
```kotlin
// Tier 1: prioritas utama — LAN-verified CARAKA peers
val lanVerified = peers.firstOrNull { it.deviceAddress in carakaLanPeerMacs 
                                      && it.status != WifiP2pDevice.CONNECTED }

// Tier 2: name-prefix filter — device dengan nama "CRK:..."
val carakaByName = peers.firstOrNull { it.isCarakaDevice()
                                       && it.status == WifiP2pDevice.AVAILABLE }
    ?: peers.firstOrNull { it.isCarakaDevice() 
                           && it.status != WifiP2pDevice.CONNECTED }

// Tier 3: fallback — tidak auto-connect ke unknown device
val candidate = lanVerified ?: carakaByName  // ← TIDAK ada "?: peers.firstOrNull()" lagi

if (candidate != null) {
    connectToPeer(candidate)
} else {
    Log.d(TAG, "No CARAKA peers found (${peers.size} non-CARAKA devices nearby, skipping)")
}
```

#### 5. Extension function `WifiP2pDevice.isCarakaDevice()`
```kotlin
private fun WifiP2pDevice.isCarakaDevice(): Boolean {
    return deviceName.startsWith("CRK:", ignoreCase = true)
        || deviceName.startsWith("CARAKA", ignoreCase = true)
}
```

#### 6. Post-connect CARAKA validation
Setelah `onConnectionInfoAvailable()` — jika 10 detik tidak ada HANDSHAKE → disconnect.
```kotlin
private var carakaValidationJob: Job? = null

private fun startCarakaValidation() {
    carakaValidationJob?.cancel()
    carakaValidationJob = scope.launch {
        delay(10_000L)
        val isCarakaConnected = repository.getConnectedPeerCount() > 0 // ada peer CARAKA?
        if (!isCarakaConnected) {
            Log.w(TAG, "No CARAKA HANDSHAKE received in 10s — disconnecting non-CARAKA device")
            manager.removeGroup(channel, ...)
            clearGroupThenDiscover()
        }
    }
}
```

### [MODIFY] `MeshSocketManager.kt`
Pastikan `onPeerConnected` di-call hanya setelah HANDSHAKE valid, bukan saat socket connect.

### [NO CHANGE] `MeshProtocol.kt`, `IdentityManager.kt`, UI screens

